# ===========================================
# Marriage — Environment Variables
# ===========================================
#
# This monorepo uses per-package .env files:
#   apps/web/.env        — Next.js app (all vars)
#   packages/db/.env     — Database package (DATABASE_URL only)
#
# Copy the .env.example in each package to get started:
#   cp apps/web/.env.example apps/web/.env
#   cp packages/db/.env.example packages/db/.env
# ===========================================
